Saffron Sales Analysis & Forecasting Project

This project analyzes saffron product sales using Python, Pandas, and data visualization techniques.
It also includes a forecasting model to identify trends and support business decisions.

 Included Files

Saffron_Sales_Report.pdf – Final business report with insights, visuals, and recommendations.
saffron_project_notebook.pdf – Complete Jupyter Notebook with code, charts, and analysis.

 Project Highlights

 Sales trend analysis

Revenue breakdown by product and region

Customer segmentation

Forecasting using time-series methods

Actionable business recommendations

